    "description": "《伊格利亚战记》是一款架空奇幻世界为背景的轻量级回合制策略游戏，采用复古精美的日式立绘与像素画风战斗相结合的经典日式美术风格。游戏以架空的奇幻世界为背景，设计了20个各具特色的势力，玩家可以成为任意势力的领主，或是通过经营经济维护城防抵御入侵守护一方，或是通过外交斡旋游说四方广纳英才合纵连横，或是通过整兵经武调兵遣将南征北伐开疆拓土，亦能上述手段并用，不断提升势力整体实力，争雄称霸，最终一统天下。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/3501b3fcc47e17724c2f0eadae575a6d.webp?t=1679663475\" width=616 height=46 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/5e939fd61ae6529fb026aae5798455d6.poster.avif?t=1679663475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/5e939fd61ae6529fb026aae5798455d6.webm?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/5e939fd61ae6529fb026aae5798455d6.mp4?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>本作脱离历史题材，立足于架空的的奇幻大世界，内有人类、矮人、精灵、兽人等种族构成的20个势力，每个势力各有不同的背景剧情。300余位英雄拥有各具特色的精美日式立绘，英雄之间错综复杂的故事随着剧情慢慢展开。像素画风战斗，复古日式美术风格，以经典的日式美术淋漓尽致表现剑与魔法组成的伊格利亚大陆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/941883e0ab1ab085f210efaccf72f355.webp?t=1679663475\" width=616 height=47 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/9df469f836a8e687bfa44af6b9c94f9d.poster.avif?t=1679663475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/9df469f836a8e687bfa44af6b9c94f9d.webm?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/9df469f836a8e687bfa44af6b9c94f9d.mp4?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>20个各具特色势力可供玩家选择。不同势力初始英雄不同，起始位置不同，具有独特效果，下辖特殊类型士兵。士兵分六大种，类型数量多达55个，可供玩家操练升级。300余位英雄下辖兵种不同，属性技能各异，玩家可通过招募、游说、俘虏劝降等多种方式纳入势力麾下。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/ff728af48181141b580931bc646228f8.webp?t=1679663475\" width=616 height=46 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/c122a15b6840f4848ab0111fc7cd7d02.poster.avif?t=1679663475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/c122a15b6840f4848ab0111fc7cd7d02.webm?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/c122a15b6840f4848ab0111fc7cd7d02.mp4?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>经营经济，维护城防，管理税收，任命大臣，举行庆典，维护民意，快节奏的回合制策略模拟，简化系统复杂度的基础上保留了策略深度，玩家可采取多种手段提升自身实力。外交谈判，合纵连横，整兵备武，攻伐四方，超过50座城池等待玩家征服。治国安民，富国强兵，与19个对手势力争雄争霸，直至统一伊格利亚大陆。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/074c2e9badbf59d3a966f05e2dcc8786.webp?t=1679663475\" width=616 height=46 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/02427033797d4dd777a30e9c2031acc2.poster.avif?t=1679663475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/02427033797d4dd777a30e9c2031acc2.webm?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116880/extras/02427033797d4dd777a30e9c2031acc2.mp4?t=1679663475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>六大兵种相互克制。战前排兵布阵，探寻最佳阵型；战斗中采用军团形式的即时战斗，指挥军团，手动释放释放英雄技能。同时还有守城攻城战，体验指挥战局，运筹帷幄的快感。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于「红手工作室」：</strong></h2>我们是一个成都的独立游戏工作室，目前由4名开发人员组成。希望借由本作展现另一个战场，一个不止有钢铁与鲜血的碰撞，还有魔法与神迹的交织的战场。让所有玩家在这个奇幻的世界中拥有不一样的体验。<br>经历了一整年的不断调优、更新，游戏终于到达了一个比较稳定的情况，纵然还有许多不足，但也希望大家会喜欢我们团队做的这第一款游戏。",
